ModuleParameters.Value: public static class Utilities { public static List<Tuple<int, double, double>> GetAUC(List<Tuple<int, long, long>> list) { list.Sort(delegate (Tuple<int, long, long> x, Tuple<int, long, long> y) { return y.Item1.CompareTo(x.Item1); });  long cum = 0; foreach (var item in list) { cum += item.Item2; }  List<Tuple<int, double, double>> output = new List<Tuple<int, double, double>>();  long numURLs = 0; long total = 0; foreach (var item in list) { numURLs += item.Item3; total += item.Item2; output.Add(new Tuple<int, double, double>(item.Item1, Math.Log10(numURLs), 1.0 * total / cum)); } return output; } }
